description:
Decorative Carved ironwood box with sea turtle carving on lid.
For more jewelry and keepsake boxes please as well as great ironwood carvings please visit TheIronwoodStore:
https://www.etsy.com/shop/TheIronwoodStore?ref=search_shop_redirect
Beautifully hand crafted ironwood keepsake box! This wood box is made with local desert ironwood that has a rich dark tone and beautiful grain. 
It is handcrafted with a detailed turtle on the top lid. We can customize your box with any other animal or design. Featured on the photos above are also our Bear head, howling Wolf, and rose. 
Just select your favorite from the drop down option menu!
Don't see the animal you are looking for? No problem! Just send us a message and we might have it in stock! If we don't we will custom make it for you, and production takes between 5-7 days. 
Dimensions are 4 inches long by 2 1/2 inches wide 
This ironwood box makes a great gift for anyone! Ironwood is heavy and sturdy and will last you a lifetime. 
Shipping- All items are sent via USPS standard flat rate shipping and is scheduled to arrive in 3-5 business days. 
Hope you enjoy browsing through or shop! If you have any questions please don't hesitate to ask, we are happy to hear from you and answer all your questions and concerns!
Best Regards always,
Desert Rose
